SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE

This license covers:
  - LLM-generated enrichment (opinion briefs, issue tags, summaries, provision tags,
    doctrinal-test assignments, Marks-provisional assignments)
  - Derived structured metadata (votes table, justice_term_scores, crosswalk tables,
    opinion_citations graph, text metrics)
  - Seed data curated by the FLexlaw team (justices, constitutional_provisions,
    doctrinal_tests tables)

This license does NOT cover:
  - Harvard CAP full opinion text — public domain, no restrictions
  - CourtListener opinion text — CC0 where applicable
  - SCDB data — redistributed under SCDB's own terms (Washington University)
  - Martin-Quinn scores — publicly available from mqscores.wustl.edu
  - Bailey ideal-point scores — publicly available from Georgetown
  - Oyez transcripts — subject to separate terms (see OYEZ_LICENSE.md)

